<HEAD>President Says Iran's Constitution is Ambiguous</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NICOSIA, Cyprus (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Iranian President Ali Khamenei said Friday
the country's constitution needs to be changed to clear up
