<HEAD>Lloyd Rees, Distinguished Artist, Dies at the Age of 93</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HOBART, Australia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Artist Lloyd Rees, known for his
romantic landscapes, died Friday at the age of 93, doctors said.
   Rees, considered one of Australia's greatest artists, recently
was named on a bicentennial list as one of the 200 greatest
