<TEXT>
   Japanese Foreign Minister Sousuke Uno completed
a three-day Washington visit Friday by meeting with U.S. lawmakers
influential in the major issues disturbing U.S.-Japan relations _
trade and defense burden-sharing.
   Uno then left via New York for Montreal, where he heads the
