<TEXT>
   Stock prices drifted lower Thursday. The Dow Jones average of 30
industrial stocks fell 12.63 to 2,101.88.
   The dollar was little changed on foreign exchange markets.
   Bond prices advanced in light trading.
   Wheat and soybean futures prices fell sharply and other grain
futures closed mostly lower; sugar futures rose sharply, energy
futures rallied and livestock and meat futures were higher.
